<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/26385554-deborah">Deborah </a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think the game of Pachinko represented life for the Koreans in Japan. There was always the hope that they would have good luck--but, as with the pac<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think the game of Pachinko represented life for the Koreans in Japan. There was always the hope that they would have good luck--but, as with the pachinko machines in the novel, someone was always making little adjustments to make sure that they never won. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
