<span id="freeTextContainer11779470261420385551">Reading this book was something like having a hard boiled egg for breakfast every day, without any salt, and maybe it&apos;s a little past its fresh-date, too, but it&apos;s good for you, and never forget that some people in this world don&apos;t get any breakfast at all.</span>
  <span id="freeText11779470261420385551" style="display:none">Reading this book was something like having a hard boiled egg for breakfast every day, without any salt, and maybe it's a little past its fresh-date, too, but it's good for you, and never forget that some people in this world don't get any breakfast at all.</span>
